parameters:
Yet the woman continued to pour her love into the boy with
zeal.

She smiled at him day and night, and when it was time to
sleep, she stayed by his side until he fell into slumber.

With his father's death and his mother's elopement, a sliver
of light seemed to be breaking through his stubbornly closed
heart.

Night. It was the time when the boy would usually fall
asleep listening to stories from a woman.

But no matter how much time passed, the woman did not
appear.

The faint sound of a woman's desperate voice from beyond the
wall made the boy understand the reason, whether he liked it
or not.

There was no longer a woman to comfort his frayed heart with
her gentle words.

Consumed by self-reproach, the boy fell asleep. He was
powerless to save the woman.

Repeating apologies in his mind that would never reach
anyone, the boy spent a sleepless night.

The next morning, the boy's figure was no longer in the
orphanage's bed.

He had slipped past the eyes of the thieves in the dead of
night and escaped from the orphanage.
